title: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
subtitle: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000, GTA+ is featuring a hoard of ghoulish benefits for members to make the most of this particularly macabre month through November 2.

- The Benefactor Terrorbyte
- Nightclub Lighting Rig and Goods Storage Upgrades
- 2X GTA$ and RP on Terrorbyte Client Jobs, 3X Nightclub Warehouse Production Speed, and 2X Supplies on Business Battles
- Free Halloween Gear
- Additional Member Bonuses

Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for full details.
